<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٧٣٨٣]</span> عَبدُ المَلكِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> بنُ فارعٍ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>عن بلالِ بنِ عبدِ اللَّهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>رَوى حَيْوةُ، عن جَعفرِ بنِ رَبيعةَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>حديثُه عنِ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> المصْريينَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
